## License Scope Clarification

This MIT License applies ONLY to the PVEScriptsLocalCustomiser tool itself:
- The import scripts (`scripts/pvescripts-import.sh`)
- The API router (`api/custom-import-router.ts`)
- The UI components (`components/CustomImportDialog.tsx`)
- The templates (`templates/*`)
- Documentation and examples

### Content Imported/Deployed Through This Tool

Content imported or deployed through this tool retains its ORIGINAL LICENSE
from its source repository. This tool does not transfer, modify, or override
the licensing of any third-party content.

When importing a project:
- The project's original license remains in effect
- Users must comply with the source project's license terms
- This tool merely facilitates deployment - it does not relicense content

### Third-Party Scripts

Scripts downloaded from community-scripts.github.io or selfh.st maintain their
original licensing (typically MIT for Proxmox community scripts).

